OL,3,C'Diogo will be with you': Jota's widow
OL,4,Curges Robertson to chase World Cup
OL,5,Cdream
OL,7,FRute Cardoso, the widow of Diogo Jota,
OL,8,Fhas urged Scotland captain Andy
OL,9,FRobertson to fulfil the World Cup
OL,10,Fdream of his former teammate in an
OL,11,Femotional letter.
OL,13,FRobertson and Jota were teammates and
OL,14,Fclose friends at Liverpool before the
OL,15,FPortuguese was killed in a car
OL,16,Faccident, aged 28, last July.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
