CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781032284
OL,3,C'Diogo will be with you': Jota's widow
OL,4,Curges Robertson to chase World Cup
OL,5,Cdream
OL,7,FAfter Scotland qualified for their
OL,8,Ffirst World Cup in almost 30 years in
OL,9,FNovember last year, Robertson revealed
OL,10,Fthat his late friend had been on his
OL,11,Fmind.
OL,13,FNow, in a video on the FIFA YouTube
OL,14,Faccount, Robertson read out a letter
OL,15,Fhe received from Jota's widow as final
OL,16,Fpreparations are underway for the
OL,17,Fstart of the World Cup in America,
OL,18,FMexico, and Canada on June 11.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781032284
OL,3,C'Diogo will be with you': Jota's widow
OL,4,Curges Robertson to chase World Cup
OL,5,Cdream
OL,7,FIn the letter, Cardoso, the mother of
OL,8,FJota's three children, wrote: "I am
OL,9,Fwriting to you with a heart full of
OL,10,Flonging, gratitude and, above all,
OL,11,Fpride.
OL,13,F"Diogo often spoke of you. Of the
OL,14,Ffriendship you built, the battles you
OL,15,Ffought together, the challenges, the
OL,16,Flaughter, the conversations about
OL,17,Ffootball... and about dreams.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781032284
OL,3,C'Diogo will be with you': Jota's widow
OL,4,Curges Robertson to chase World Cup
OL,5,Cdream
OL,7,F"The World Cup was one of those
OL,8,Fdreams, a dream that the two of you
OL,9,Fnurtured, side by side, with the same
OL,10,Fpassion with which you took to the
OL,11,Fpitch.
OL,13,F"When I heard your words and learnt
OL,14,Fwhat you felt on that day when
OL,15,FScotland qualified for the World Cup,
OL,16,Fafter so many years of waiting, I
OL,17,Frealised that Diogo never truly left
OL,18,Fthe pitch.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781032284
OL,3,C'Diogo will be with you': Jota's widow
OL,4,Curges Robertson to chase World Cup
OL,5,Cdream
OL,7,F"By achieving that moment and securing
OL,8,Fyour place at the World Cup, you won't
OL,9,Fbe going alone. You'll be taking his
OL,10,Fdream with you too. And when you step
OL,11,Fonto the pitch, I know it won't just
OL,12,Fbe you walking out, Diogo will be with
OL,13,Fyou in your thoughts, in your steps,
OL,14,Fin your heart.
OL,16,F"So today, I want to thank you. Thank
OL,17,Fyou for not forgetting him. Thank you
OL,18,Ffor taking him with you. Thank you for
OL,19,Fturning the pain of loss into strength
OL,20,Fand into something so beautiful.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781032284
OL,3,C'Diogo will be with you': Jota's widow
OL,4,Curges Robertson to chase World Cup
OL,5,Cdream
OL,7,F"That's how we do it here at home too.
OL,8,FEvery day. He would be, and is,
OL,9,Fincredibly proud of you. Cherish that
OL,10,Fdream, Andy. Live it for yourself and
OL,11,Ffor him."
OL,13,FIn response, Robertson said the letter
OL,14,Fwill "stay with me for a very long
OL,15,Ftime".
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781032284
OL,3,C'Diogo will be with you': Jota's widow
OL,4,Curges Robertson to chase World Cup
OL,5,Cdream
OL,7,FThe 32-year-old, who is moving to
OL,8,FTottenham this summer, says in the
OL,9,Fvideo: "It's obviously amazing of Rute
OL,10,Fto even take the time, for what she's
OL,11,Fgoing through, to write me a letter,
OL,12,Fbut it just sums up the person that
OL,13,Fshe is. Thankfully, I got to know her
OL,14,Fand the amazing times that they had.
OL,16,FHe adds: "I'll carry him in my heart
OL,17,Fand I know he'll be with me come the
OL,18,Ffirst game, come the second game, come
OL,19,Fthe third game and hopefully beyond
OL,20,Fthat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781032284
OL,3,C'Diogo will be with you': Jota's widow
OL,4,Curges Robertson to chase World Cup
OL,5,Cdream
OL,7,F"He's always there. The memories are
OL,8,Falways something that we bring up and
OL,9,Fsometimes laugh, sometimes cry.
OL,11,F"And that will be no different,
OL,12,Fespecially going into a tournament
OL,13,Fwhich is full of emotion. I know he'll
OL,14,Fbe right at the front of my mind.
OL,16,F"I'm not only just playing for me, I'm
OL,17,Fplaying for both of us."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
